\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7043539 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11500731\charrsid3306671 Oh no. No. But it just happened he was there that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14100231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11500731\charrsid3306671 In fact with those long hours I don't suppose you saw him much at all really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7043539 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11500731\charrsid3306671 No. No, he used to get home about sevenish. I don't know, early in the morning we 
