\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7043539 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11500731\charrsid3306671 I think there was only two rooms. It looked out onto the Jamaica Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14100231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11500731\charrsid3306671 Do you mean one bedroom and one sort of living room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7043539 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11500731\charrsid3306671 Yes, I should imagine - I know we had two rooms. Fifty-five Russell Scott Buildings
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14100231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11500731\charrsid3306671 It must have been very crowded there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7043539 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11500731\charrsid3306671 Well - I - I don't think we - oh I don't - I w
ouldn't know - I've forgotten. I've forgotten. I know I was tiny. And - the baby in the pram, pushchair, there was - it was - London flats are not the same as - the flats now. They were buildings. It was Russell Scott Buildings, and those buildings she us
e
d to - she did say to me, well - I don't - it must have been Charlie I suppose, the next boy, is I could only have been about six. Anyway, take the baby down in the pram and play with him in the yard, the playground. And I did, I let it go and it went rou
nd and round and round to the centre and tipped up. I still have a horror over that. But of course what could the women do in those days? I mean, we wouldn't dream - oh well I wouldn't - although }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6104996\charrsid3306671 these mother's}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11500731\charrsid3306671  do, they let their kids out all day. Oh, I fee
l, they do, probably they do love them the same. But that was - I always remember this it must have been - Charlie, the next boy, 'cos there was only me, unless she'd got another baby.
