tle, he was - and then she had the twins in Anchor Street, because she - wed in the kitchen - we moved in and we had to do the - wallpapering. We - but we did it, I helped mum, I was only tiny but we helped. 'Course they were smaller rooms - lower than th
is. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4871271\charrsid3306671 And after we'd got the twins, I - she named them the flowers, Rosina and Violet. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11500731\charrsid3306671 
