. Oh yes, I - I never stopped them. If they wanted - they had their own rooms anyway. One for their hobby and one for their - their bedroom, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10973898\charrsid3306671 box room}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
