\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7043539 LC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11500731\charrsid3306671 No. No, you'd be surprised, my husband didn't like music halls. But I did take }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
